textBeforeTable: Xeon® E5 Family Boards / Socket R3 (LGA 2011) [ top ] The new Supermicro's X10 UP Serverboards offer the latest Xeon E5-2600/1600 v3 technology solutions with the highest levels of performance in different form factors to meet various application needs. X10SRL-F, with 7x PCIe (up to 5x PCIe 3.0 x8) slots onboard, is the best choice to maximize your I/O intensive application demand. On the other hand, X10SRi-F offers the latest virtualization support at low cost. For customers who need multiple I/O solutions in a 1U chassis, X10SRW-F (up to 3x AOC) and X10SRG-F (up to 5x AOC) provide the ultimate solutions. Supermicro's first UP Storage serverboard, X10SRH-CF/-CLN4F, brings the latest SAS3 (12Gb/s data rate) technology to the market with the best performance per dollar value.
